author: codex-sdk-boundary-20260722
acceptance_criteria: "Default standard-depth get/show JSON reports notes_count whenever notes are omitted; full/deep projections remain backward compatible and include notes; CLI aliases, SDK result contracts, MCP projections, TOON/JSON docs, and contract fixtures remain coherent; regression tests cover zero, one, and multiple notes plus explicit depth modes"
parent: pm-mpbb
reporter: GitHub GH-645
severity: medium
expected_result: "Standard-depth structured output makes omitted note context explicit through notes_count and depth/projection metadata, or includes the notes consistently."
actual_result: Default standard-depth JSON omits notes and exposes neither notes_count nor a signal that note context was projected out.
